Question
The following is a section of resources related to questions
--

Get a list of existing questions
GET /api/questions
< 200
< Content-Type: application/json
[
    {
        pk: 1,
        model: "sinq3.question",
        fields: {
            text: "Why are rubber bands stretchy?"
        }
    }, 
    {
        pk: 3,
        model: "sinq3.question",
        fields: {
            text: "Why are carrots orange?"
        }
    }, 
]

Create a new question
POST /api/questions/create
> Content-Type: application/json
{
    cause: "I pulled it apart.",
    effect: "Rubber bands stretch."
}
< 200
{
    "status": "created",
    "url": "/causeandeffects/1"
}

Get a list of the images associated with the specified question
GET /api/questions/1/images
< 200
[
    {
        pk: 1,
        model: "sinq3.questionimage",
        fields: {
            date_created: "2012-11-27T20:19:26.740Z",
            image: "images/questions/cdv_photo_018.jpg",
            question: 1,
            date_last_modified: "2012-11-27T20:19:26.740Z"
        }
    }
]

Create a new image for the specified question
POST /api/questions/1/images/create
> Content-Type: multipart/form-data
{
    "data": "base64_image_data"
}
< 200
{
    "status": "created",
    "url": "/questions/1/images/2"
}

